BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Monty Python's Spamalot
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T220000
DTSTAMP:20260720T203550Z
UID:occ-489@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Eric Idle's Tony-winning Arthurian spoof — killer rabbits\, 
 taunting Frenchmen\, coconut-shell hoofbeats — in a national touring pro
 duction.\n\nKing Arthur recruits his knights and quests for the Grail past
  killer rabbits\, taunting French soldiers\, the Knights Who Say Ni\, and 
 a Lady of the Lake who resents her lack of stage time. Eric Idle adapted t
 he Pythons' 1975 Holy Grail film into a musical\, writing the songs with J
 ohn Du Prez\, including "Always Look on the Bright Side of Life." The orig
 inal 2005 Broadway production won three Tony Awards\, Best Musical among t
 hem. This is a national touring production.
GEO:33.7726136;-84.3853395
LAST-MODIFIED:20260720T203536Z
LOCATION:Fox Theatre\, 660 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://foxtheatre.evenue.net/cgi-bin/ncommerce3/SEGetGroupList?groupC
 ode=SPA&linkID=fta&shopperContext=&caller=&appCode=
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Wizard of Oz
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T213000
DTSTAMP:20260720T203550Z
UID:occ-1427@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:The 1939 MGM songbook onstage\, Toto played by a puppet\, from
  Walton County's community theatre.\n\nThe stage adaptation of the 1939 MG
 M film\, with the Harold Arlen and E. Y. Harburg songs intact\, 'Over the 
 Rainbow' included. A Kansas farm girl is swept into Oz and heads down the 
 yellow brick road with a scarecrow\, a tin man\, and a cowardly lion\, hop
 ing the Wizard can send her home. In this production Toto is a puppet in t
 he Lion King mold\, and the Munchkins are played mostly by children. Marc 
 Hammes directs for On Stage Playhouse\, Walton County's community theatre\
 ; runs through July 26.
GEO:33.7934843;-83.7059787
LAST-MODIFIED:20260720T203541Z
LOCATION:On Stage Playhouse\, 215 High School Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.tickettailor.com/events/onstageinc/2277622
END:VEVENT
