BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cinderella - Prince Street Players Version
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260724T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260724T220000
DTSTAMP:20260720T203550Z
UID:occ-1663@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:The Prince Street Players musical of Perrault's Cinderella\, s
 taged by Winder-Barrow's Children's PLAYhouse with an all-ages cast.\n\nA 
 musical retelling of Charles Perrault's fairy tale\, the one with the cind
 ers\, the slipper\, and the midnight deadline\, in the Prince Street Playe
 rs version: adaptation and lyrics by Jim Eiler\, music by Eiler and Jeanne
  Bargy. Billie Nye-Muller directs a community cast of children and adults 
 for Winder-Barrow Community Theatre's Children's PLAYhouse. Proceeds from 
 the show support Feeding Barrow\, a weekend meal program for Barrow County
  students. Runs through July 26.
GEO:33.9908372;-83.7196428
LAST-MODIFIED:20260720T203549Z
LOCATION:Winder Cultural Arts Center\, 105 E Athens St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.tix.com/ticket-sales/winderbarrowtheatre/5602/event/146334
 7
END:VEVENT
