 ers\, the slipper\, and the midnight deadline\, in the Prince Street Playe
 rs version: adaptation and lyrics by Jim Eiler\, music by Eiler and Jeanne
  Bargy. Billie Nye-Muller directs a community cast of children and adults 
 for Winder-Barrow Community Theatre's Children's PLAYhouse. Proceeds from 
