CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Lin-Manuel Miranda's hip-hop biography of Alexander Hamilton\,
  on national tour.\n\nLin-Manuel Miranda's musical about Alexander Hamilto
 n\, the orphaned immigrant who wrote his way into the American Revolution 
 and the founding of the nation. The score moves through hip-hop\, R&B\, an
 d jazz\, drawing on Ron Chernow's biography for its history. Winner of 11 
 Tony Awards and the Pulitzer Prize for Drama\, with direction by Thomas Ka
 il and choreography by Andy Blankenbuehler. A national touring production.
