BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Winter Wonderettes
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261205T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261205T220000
DTSTAMP:20260720T203550Z
UID:occ-1612@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Roger Bean's holiday sequel to The Marvelous Wonderettes: girl
 -group harmonies at a hardware store party\, and Santa's gone missing.\n\n
 A holiday installment of Roger Bean's Marvelous Wonderettes jukebox musica
 ls\, with the four girls in tight harmony providing the entertainment at H
 arper's Hardware annual holiday party. When Santa turns up missing\, they 
 improvise their way to saving the night. The setlist leans on seasonal sta
 ndards like "Santa Claus Is Comin' to Town\," "Jingle Bell Rock\," and "Ru
 n\, Rudolph\, Run." From Stage Door Theatre.
GEO:33.9447222;-84.3319444
LAST-MODIFIED:20260720T203547Z
LOCATION:Stage Door Theatre\, 5339 Chamblee Dunwoody Rd
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://ci.ovationtix.com/36385/performance/11825788/selecttickets
END:VEVENT
